name: BioMark
paragraph: Genotype calling was carried out using the SDS 2.3 software (Life Technologies, Carlsbad California) or the BioMark 3.0.2 software (Fluidigm, South San Francisco, California)

name: Factoshiny
paragraph: Factoshiny package running within RStudio platform was used for HCPC (48, 49).

name: vhica
paragraph: "The ENC values of the S, M, L segments of the CCHF virus were calculated in R Studio programming software, ""vhica"" library [13]"

name: HH
paragraph: Statements evaluated with a forced Likert scale were plotted using package “HH” [23] in the open-source software program R [24].

name: locfit
paragraph: Statistical analyses were performed using R (Version 3.5.1, R Core Team 2018 [88]; locfit package version 1.5-9.1 [89]; ggplot2 package [90] for visualizations) with α set to 0.05.
